            "title": "Freedom Capital看好餐飲股Dutch Bros與墨西哥烤雞連鎖El Pollo Loco",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oNhcpSkIY5a9iGvzI6sR4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEM4J18N_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Freedom Capital Markets週三對五家餐飲企業啟動研究覆蓋，給予Dutch Bros、<span>First Watch餐廳集團</span>及El Pollo Loco「買入」評級，同時以「持有」評級啟動對CAVA集團及Kura Sushi USA的覆蓋。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Lynne <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Collier\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Collier;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Collier\">Collier</a>以95美元的目標價啟動對Dutch Bros的覆蓋，意味著約33%的上漲空間。Collier指出，該公司擁有「獨特的企業文化、龐大的市場拓展空間、業內領先的現金回報率，以及即將推出食品菜單等多項業績催化劑」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7f7e2a73-54bb-3347-abb6-e3bc954f562a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">First Watch餐廳集團獲得「買入」評級及17美元目標價，潛在漲幅約31%。Collier將First Watch形容為「早午餐優質餐飲品類中的新興領導者，回報表現優異，成長跑道漫長」，並補充指出近期股價回調已創造出具吸引力的入場時機。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">El Pollo Loco獲「買入」評級，目標價22美元，同樣意味著約33%的上行空間。Collier稱其為「一個尚未受到市場廣泛關注的標的，管理層相對較新，正積極推進轉型策略，同店銷售持續改善，新店擴張步伐亦在加快」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於CAVA集團，Collier以「持有」評級啟動覆蓋，目標價95美元。儘管公司基本面強勁，但估值偏高——未來十二個月EV/EBITDA達44.2倍——因此建議等待更佳入場時機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>Kura Sushi</span></span> USA同樣獲「持有」評級，目標價68美元。Collier指出，該公司同店銷售可預測性有限，而未來十二個月EV/EBITDA約22倍的估值水平下，風險與回報已趨於平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
